-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17355,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/28\/muslims-abandon-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33665,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Time will come when Muslims abandon Sunnah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miqdam ibn Ma\u2019dikarib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI have surely been given the Quran and something similar along with it. Soon, the time will come when a man will recline on his couch, saying: Only follow the Quran, make lawful what you\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33649,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/25\/ahmad-enjoin-maruf-rifq\/","url_meta":{"origin":33665,"position":5},"title":"Ahmad on Amr: Enjoin good, forbid evil with humble gentleness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 25, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhanna reported: I asked Abu Abdullah Imam Ahmad, may Allah have mercy on him, about enjoining good and forbidding evil, \u201cHow should one enjoin it?\u201d Ahmad said, \u201cOne should enjoin good with gentleness and humility. If they make him hear what he dislikes, he should not get angry such that\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/